commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: Wow, look at this.

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: W-Wait, what's up with this?

commands.speaker: Honoka
commands.line: I wanted everyone to get a little closer, so we planned a party! Let's put all the small stuff aside and enjoy ourselves today!

commands.speaker: Dia
commands.line: A surprise party? Exactly as I expected.

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: You'd picked up on it?

commands.speaker: Dia
commands.line: It's an easy guess to make, looking at how you've been acting over the past few days.

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: Was I that obvious?!

commands.speaker: Dia
commands.line: Still, it's not every day you get to have a party, so I'll be enjoying myself.

commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: The decorations are so sparkly and pretty. I love them.

commands.speaker: Ayumu
commands.line: Thanks, I'm flattered to hear you say that.

commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: You made these, Ayumu? They're beautiful.

commands.speaker: Ayumu
commands.line: It wasn't just me--we all pulled together and worked hard, so I'm delighted you like them. Let's have lots of fun today.

commands.speaker: You
commands.line: All right, everyone! I made lots of food, so dig in!

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: What's that, a soba omelet?

commands.speaker: You
commands.line: They're Niceoodles. Try them; you'll be jonesing for more.

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: Well, someone's awfully confident. I'll give them a try, then. And I'll say now that you're not satisfying me with second-rate noodles.

commands.speaker: You
commands.line: Well, have a taste first.

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: Fine, here goes. Om...mmm?!

commands.speaker: You
commands.line: How is it?

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: W-Well, not bad, I'd say. Better than I thought, even.

commands.speaker: Honoka
commands.line: Nico, you can't even stop yourself from eating more.

commands.speaker: Kotori
commands.line: There are sweets, too, everyone, so eat up!

commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: Sweets! There are so many cute ones.

commands.speaker: Kotori
commands.line: There's plenty, so have as many as you like.

commands.speaker: Rina
commands.line: I don't know which one to start with.

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: The mikan hotpot is great, too, so eat up plenty!

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: I'll pass.

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: Huh? Wh-Why?!

commands.speaker: Nico
commands.line: It's fine, really.

commands.speaker: Chika
commands.line: Whuh?! Hey, don't knock it before you try it!

commands.speaker: Honoka
commands.line: Ahaha, well, let's have a ton of fun today and recharge our energy! Then, let's make the School Idol Festival a success!

commands.speaker: Everyone
commands.line: Yeah!
